name: Buttercup Minky Ruffle Pants
description: These pants come in a dark pink, super soft Minky fabric.  They have 3 layers of fluffy, brown giraffe print ruffles across the bottom and a rouched band at bottom of leg.  These pants have an elastic waistband, for easy dressing.  Buttercup pants can be custom made in sizes 3 month to 5T.  Perfect accompaniment to the pants is the circle applique initial top that can be found in another listing.

name: Circle Applique Initial shirt
description: This top can be custom made in sizes ranging from 3 month to 12 years.  It has a circle disk applique in hot pink minky dot for the background and brown giraffe print for the initial.  Initials are in lower case letters.  T-shirts are "Monag" brand and come in short or long sleeves.  Please specify size and sleeve length in notes to seller on "Paypal".  Pairs with Minky Buttercup Pants in another listing.

name: Fall 2011 Clover Dress- Reverse Knot Dress
description:
This dress is made from quality, designer fabrics.  It is similiar to the well known "Knot Top", but comes in dress form.  The dress ties in back through 2 buttonholes.  This dress is custom made for your child in my smoke free home.  

Sizes Available 12 month - 12 year
